{"tid":1169262,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"其實日月神教係咪即係明教分裂出黎??","createTime":"2019-05-24T09:04:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T13:32:17.000Z","uid":58335,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"582d8c0f81c625d7ff82a6d8c3f59958b998766c","tid":1169262,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T09:04:19.000Z","msg":"維基咁講:<br />\n日月神教（在舊版金庸小說稱為朝陽神教）是金庸武俠小說《笑傲江湖》的虛構組織，[1]<span style=\"color: red;\">但沒有任何證據顯示傳自《倚天屠龍記》中的明教</span><br />\n<br />\n但呢篇野又分析到幾似層層<br />\n<ins><a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/history/48o6e2.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fhistory%2F48o6e2.html&d=vKriUNUS%2F8bMVR7j%2Bz3ffg5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=92be1555\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/history/48o6e2.html</a></ins><br />\n<br />\n大家點睇?"},{"pid":"37e4350951b5c6130339dbce992ce9454e9fb1bf","tid":1169262,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T10:00:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b267bee13138372cdf19625f93b6d330c7da317a","tid":1169262,"uid":3976,"like":38,"dislike":2,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T10:02:50.000Z","msg":"你係光明左使都唔知 我地點知"},{"pid":"b407440396ae78c34689154db2d81be33ea1f953","tid":1169262,"uid":58335,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"b267bee13138372cdf19625f93b6d330c7da317a","tid":1169262,"uid":3976,"like":38,"dislike":2,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T10:02:50.000Z","msg":"你係光明左使都唔知 我地點知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T10:11:48.000Z","msg":"個時我死左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b001f04744d83b617f1c93de1a1b19c0e800d35a","tid":1169262,"uid":23400,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T10:15:51.000Z","msg":"琴日略略考究過，話喺金庸既世界裡係一個光明，一個黑暗，兩個制度上相似，有左使同拜火，但應該唔係由明教分裂出來"},{"pid":"838a3d262dbada5023c6aabf83db0cb65a8933db","tid":1169262,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b001f04744d83b617f1c93de1a1b19c0e800d35a","tid":1169262,"uid":23400,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T10:15:51.000Z","msg":"琴日略略考究過，話喺金庸既世界裡係一個光明，一個黑暗，兩個制度上相似，有左使同拜火，但應該唔係由明教分裂出來"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T10:24:04.000Z","msg":"但兩者係正派眼中都係魔教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢段好似講得幾好<br />\n<br />\n可我們知道，每一個門派的創立，都是經過無數高手的嘔心瀝血和多代志士仁人的打拚，經過上百年的淬鍊，才能立足於武林之中的。江湖中的各大門派無不是如此。日月神教要是沒有基礎，不可能一步登天，成為當時的第一大組織吧？唯一能解釋的就是：它繼承了明教，在明教的基礎之上才發展壯大起來的。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/history/48o6e2.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fhistory%2F48o6e2.html&d=vKriUNUS%2F8bMVR7j%2Bz3ffg5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=92be1555\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/history/48o6e2.html</a>"},{"pid":"7ab6164ea3c415459993b74abf25a6def9f880ba","tid":1169262,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T10:42:52.000Z","msg":"左使瓜之前整咗吸星大法，日月神教又咁啱有七星大法"},{"pid":"14788c104eadf4e25f4ae99e32f6fc69f5f1a44b","tid":1169262,"uid":190617,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"838a3d262dbada5023c6aabf83db0cb65a8933db","tid":1169262,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b001f04744d83b617f1c93de1a1b19c0e800d35a","tid":1169262,"uid":23400,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T10:15:51.000Z","msg":"琴日略略考究過，話喺金庸既世界裡係一個光明，一個黑暗，兩個制度上相似，有左使同拜火，但應該唔係由明教分裂出來"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T10:24:04.000Z","msg":"但兩者係正派眼中都係魔教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢段好似講得幾好<br />\n<br />\n可我們知道，每一個門派的創立，都是經過無數高手的嘔心瀝血和多代志士仁人的打拚，經過上百年的淬鍊，才能立足於武林之中的。江湖中的各大門派無不是如此。日月神教要是沒有基礎，不可能一步登天，成為當時的第一大組織吧？唯一能解釋的就是：它繼承了明教，在明教的基礎之上才發展壯大起來的。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：